(Not an allience symbol, but possably pred since they are not 
maximal.)

::Feline::

She smiled. "Good, that will complete the disguise. Skulletron, would 
you be so kind as to help me put on the," she shivers,"maximal 
symbol."

She looked at Zardus. "Yes, for this mission, the reward should be 
well worth it." She walked up to him, traced a claw down his chest 
and lower down to across his thigh. "Yes, well worth the risks." She 
smiled and walked over to Skulletron. "Well, let's get this show 
going."
